{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">We fused <strong>turn-based strategy</strong> and <strong>horde survival</strong> on a <strong>hex grid</strong> to create one of the most satisfying and endlessly replayable <strong>roguelike deckbuilders</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3463290/extras/Intro2-gif-crop-optimize2.gif?t=1739418067\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unleash powerful <strong>hex-based cards</strong> to wipe out cyber threats with strategic formations, applying status effects like frost, earthquake or poison.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3463290/extras/Level-up3-gif-crop-optimize.gif?t=1739418067\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Clear the grid to collect gems and use them to add, remove, or upgrade cards in your deck. Experiment with a wide variety of <strong>synergies and combos</strong> to build the ultimate deck.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3463290/extras/enemies-gif-crop-optimize.gif?t=1739418067\" />Encounter cyber threats like <strong>trojan horses, adware, and more</strong>, as they take on diverse forms, multiply rapidly, and attack with unique patterns.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3463290/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739418067","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3463290/page.bg.jpg?t=1739418067","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3463290/bef557fc38c7323c074ccd8e4ce94bcccfc1e373/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739418067","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3463290/bef557fc38c7323c074ccd8e4ce94bcccfc1e373/capsule_184x69.